Directory contents and code structure
-------------------------------------

Provided code modules

apf.cpp       : Main module
solve.cpp     : Solver code. This is where the heavy lifting is done
init.cpp      : Reads command line arguments and initializes the simulation,
              : alllocating data structures
cmdLine.cpp   : Parses command line arugments
Report.cpp    : Reports various information
format.cpp    : Program showing how to adjust output formatting for C++ ostream 
             
Timer.cpp     : Serial Timer
parTimer.cpp  : Parallel version of the Timer

splot.c       : plotter
printMat.c    : utility to print out a 2D array

***************************************************************************
*** You should not the following files (nor their names)
*** Doing so could could cause your submission to be graded incorrectly
***************************************************************************

cmdLine.cpp
Report.cpp
Timer.cpp
parTimer.cpp
splot.c
apf.h
types.h


------------------------------------------------------------------

Scripts showing how to invoke the program

run.sh                          Serial run
